Package: podr
Type: Package
Title: Simple Method For Reading And Cleaning Podcast Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ernesto Ramirez <er.ramirez@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Ernesto Ramirez <er.ramirez@gmail.com>
Description: Given a podcast rss feed, these functions can perofrm two
    operations. readpod will parse and save all available episode data.
    cleanpod will clean up the data frame created by readpod and reduce 
    variables to podcast title, episode title, date of publication, and 
    show duration. 
Imports:
    xml2,
    dplyr,
    magrittr,
    purrr,
    stringr,
    lubridate
URL:  https://github.com/erramirez/podr/
BugReports: https://github.com/erramirez/podr/issues
